      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Residual norm <1e-8 at convergence; contact penetration <0.001 mm.",
      "rationale": "Newton-Raphson iteration converged to residual norm 3.2e-10 for all load steps. Augmented Lagrange contact algorithm maintained penetration below 4e-4 mm. No spurious oscillations observed in force-displacement curves."
